text: "Over and Over Again" is a song by English recording artist Nathan Sykes. The song was written by Sykes and was released in the United Kingdom on 20 November 2015 as the second single from his debut studio album. The song peaked to number 8 on the UK Singles Chart. Sykes performed the song live on The X Factor on 22 November 2015. ==Charts== Chart (2015) Peak position ==References== Category:2015 songs
